{
  "id": "stanford-wh592zr8117",
  "dct_title_s": "Aerial Photographs. Barberton Greenbelt area, South Africa, geologic survey",
  "dct_description_sm": [
    "Donald Lowe, Stanford Professor in Earth Sciences, Emeritus, conducted geological research in the Barberton Greenbelt area in South Africa. His work produced a comprehensive geological map of the west-central part of the Greenstone belt. Dr Lowe used a series of aerial photographs as the basis for mapping out the geological structures of the belt. This project’s objective is to digitize and georeference Dr Lowe’s annotated aerial photographs."
  ],
